+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js v24.18.0
+- packageManager: npm v12.0.1
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run`
+- focused: `npx cucumber-js {scenario}`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js`
+- coverage: `npx c8 --exclude-after-remapping false --reporter=text npx cucumber-js`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage-json`
+- plank-inventory: `node -e "const fs=require('fs');const patt=/@planks(-provisionally)?\(['\"]([^'\"]+)['\"]\)/g;['src'].forEach(d=>fs.readdirSync(d).filter(f=>f.endsWith('.js')).forEach(f=>{const m=fs.readFileSync(d+'/'+f,'utf8');let b;while((b=patt.exec(m))!==null)console.log(b[1]?'PROVISIONAL:'+b[2]:'PLANK:'+b[2]);}))"`
+- typecheck: `node --check`
+- lint: none (no lint tool configured; gap: consider biome or eslint for the project)
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: `@logic tier runs against local Node.js runtime with no credential`
+- weather: coverage/coverage.json
+- runrecord: none
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: locked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber (dev)
+- dependency: c8 (dev, installed for coverage; not declared in package.json)
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
+
+## Methodology checks
+
+- watchbill-conformance: required, derived as @captain @conformance skeleton
+- perturbation-quiescence: required, derived as @captain @conformance skeleton
+- plank-join: none (token-search plank-inventory is not a join source; step-usage provides the join)
+- plank-form: none (token-search plank-inventory; plank-form rules deferred to verification-conformance rule set)
+- forbidden-doubles: none (no @exceptional-double marks present)
+- scantling-reference: none (no scantlings declared)
+- feature-lint: none (no .gplintrc or equivalent)
+- budget: none (no budget ceiling set)
+- verification-conformance: none (scantlings path is none; rule set deferred)
